title: Gentilly: Work in Progress
name: Gentilly: Work in Progress
description:
A Map by Dgillmor

The Gentilly District of New Orleans is coming back, slowly. Students from the University of California, Berkeley, &lt;a href=&quot;http://journalism.berkeley.edu&quot;&gt;Graduate School of Journalism&lt;/a&gt; traveled to New Orleans to visit the district and interview some of its residents. Here's what we found.
